title: Michael Mind Project
text:
The Michael Mind Project (MMP) is a German house DJ and music production duo consisting of Jens Kindervater and Frank BÃ¼lles. Formed in 2007 under the name Michael Mind, it took its current name in 2009 to avoid confusion and emphasize the fictional nature of the name.


== Biography ==
In 2008, The Michael Mind Project released a track called "Show Me Love", a new version of the hit of Robin S. This track was a real success in Clubs, concerts and on YouTube as well.
